column5: Heading up for the long weekend, Whitestone isnt in my Navionics chip.  Anyone have a map with some depths?  Thanks!

Im not sure if Duck Rock  is open,or under a different name,but they had a map in the the lounge. Check with the guy across the street from them, on the river.  He,s a good fella.Ask lots of questions.
Thanks! The cottage I've rented is right next to duck rock.
Duck Rock is open. You could try Angler's Atlas for a free map once you've signed up:  http://www.anglersatlas.com/mapsearch/googlemap/ON/
